Whenever we deploy our code, we aren’t getting the usual pop ups telling us that everything is connected. Instead our riolog is blank, and we can’t print anything to it. I have already restarted the computer as well as looking throught the code and I can’t find an issue. Any help would be much appriciated.

R_B:

Any help would be much appreciated.

Is sympathy of any help? We’ve seen random appearances and disappearances of the riolog for years. Haven’t found a pattern despite hundreds of data points! Often it’ll work fine and then with the next deploy won’t show or update if already showing and doesn’t reappear for hours or even days. Seems like I created an issue years ago but I’m not sure.
